      "span_text": "Although this result shows that cooperative binding is a feature of both specific and non-specific interactions, the fact that the specific stoichiometry is limited to 2:1 while non-specific complexes are often larger  , suggests that the 6mG-specific complex may be structurally distinct from those formed on lesion-free DNA. An additional striking feature of the 6mG complexes is their low stability relative to non-specific interactions."
